title: NFL ATL: Draft preview with Greg Cosell
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Draft preview with Greg Cosell
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- checks in with NFL Films senior producer Greg Cosell to break down this year’s most intriguing draft prospects.  Elsewhere, the gang goes over all the latest headlines around the league and one member of Studio 66 gets a very special surprise.
